Class DictHandler

    • DictHandler
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CreateDictFromEpilont, CreateDictFromEPISEM, CreateDictFromEpSO, CreateDictFromESSO, CreateDictFromFENICS

    public abstract class DictHandler
extends Object
    DictHandler is the common super class for the conversion of ontology resources into dictionary files that can be loaded by the UIMA Analysis Engine ConceptMapper
